#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:9
msgid "ブログ運用にAblogを活用する"
msgstr "Utilize Ablog for blog operation"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:11
msgid "純粋なSphinxの機能よりも、もう少しブログっぽく運用したい場合にAblogを活用すると便利"
msgstr ""
"It is useful to use Ablog when you want to operate it more like a blog than "
"pure Sphinx functions."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:14
msgid "Ablogとは"
msgstr "What is Ablog?"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:15
msgid ""
"sphinxの拡張機能で、ブログのような形式で記事を管理できる。カテゴリやタグを設定しておけば、それに基づいて記事一覧を生成してくれるのが便利。"
msgstr ""
"With the sphinx extension, you can manage articles in a blog-like format. If"
" you set categories and tags, it is convenient to generate a list of "
"articles based on them."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:18
msgid "Ablogでできるようになること"
msgstr "What you can do with Ablog"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:19
msgid "カテゴリやタグで記事を分類"
msgstr "Sort articles by category or tag"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:20
msgid "記事一覧の自動生成"
msgstr "Automatic generation of article list"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:21
#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:65
msgid "自動アーカイブ"
msgstr "automatic archiving"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:22
#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:82
msgid "サイドバーサポート"
msgstr "sidebar support"

