#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:105
msgid "ドラフト記事の作成"
msgstr "Creating a draft article"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:26
msgid "Ablogのインストール"
msgstr "Installing Ablog"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:27
msgid ""
"pipやposetry addでインストールし、conf.pyを少しいじればすぐ使える。`詳細は公式ドキュメント参照 "
"<https://ablog.readthedocs.io>`_"
msgstr ""
"You can install it with pip or posery add and use it immediately by "
"modifying conf.py a little. `For details, refer to the official document "
"<https://ablog.readthedocs.io>`_"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:31
msgid "記事作成"
msgstr "Article creation"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-03-27-001-ablog-install.rst:33
msgid ""
"blogフォルダを作成し、その中に記事を作成。ファイルは手動作成でもよいし ``ablog post new-post`` で作成してもよい。"
msgstr ""
"Create a blog folder and write articles in it. The file can be created "
"manually or with ``ablog post new-post``."

